OL,3,CMan murdered ex-wife as she put
OL,4,Cflowers on their son's grave, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FA 68-year-old man armed himself with a
OL,8,F12-inch kitchen knife and laid in wait
OL,9,Fat a cemetery before stabbing his ex-
OL,10,Fwife to death at the graveside of
OL,11,Ftheir son, a court has heard.
OL,13,FMartin Suter, of Lee-on-the-Solent,
OL,14,Fpleaded guilty to the murder of 71-
OL,15,Fyear-old Ann Blackwood at Crofton
OL,16,FCemetery in Stubbington, Hampshire, on
OL,17,FJuly 24 2023, which would have been
OL,18,Fthe 36th birthday of their son
OL,19,FChristopher.
