OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe court heard that Christopher took
OL,8,Fhis own life in 2003 and the couple
OL,9,Fhad divorced in 2004.
OL,11,FThe defendant admitted his guilt on
OL,12,Fthe first day of his trial in May 2024
OL,13,Fbut the case is only now proceeding
OL,14,Ftowards sentencing after a trial on
OL,15,Fseparate indecent assault charges
OL,16,Fconcluded.
