OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FHe pleaded guilty in May 2023 to one
OL,8,Foffence of indecent assault of a girl
OL,9,Funder 14 years but was later acquitted
OL,10,Fof six further charges at Bolton Crown
OL,11,FCourt.
OL,13,FA Newton hearing is being held at
OL,14,FPortsmouth Crown Court to determine
OL,15,Fwhether Suter took the kitchen knife
OL,16,Fto the scene and whether he intended
OL,17,Fto kill Ms Blackwood or cause grievous
OL,18,Fbodily harm.
