OL,4,Cflowers on their son's grave, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FRobert O'Sullivan KC, prosecuting,
OL,8,Fsaid Suter drove his Mazda MX5 car to
OL,9,Fthe cemetery and arrived with a bunch
OL,10,Fof flowers at about 10.30am, about
OL,11,Ffive hours before his ex-wife.
OL,13,FAnalysis of phone GPS data showed him
OL,14,Fat the cemetery at 10.30am and again
OL,15,Fat 2.30pm.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
