OL,3,CMan murdered ex-wife as she put
OL,4,Cflowers on their son's grave, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMr O'Sullivan said: "The defendant
OL,8,Fstabbed her in the back with a kitchen
OL,9,Fknife and, the blade having broken
OL,10,Foff, he repeatedly stabbed her in the
OL,11,Fneck with a pair of scissors that she
OL,12,Fhad brought with her to cut the
OL,13,Fflowers she had planned to put on her
OL,14,Fson's grave."
OL,16,FHe said that at 3.39pm, Suter called
OL,17,F999 and told police: "I have just
OL,18,Fkilled my ex-wife, I have just stabbed
OL,19,Fher to death."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
