OL,3,CMan murdered ex-wife as she put
OL,4,Cflowers on their son's grave, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FMr O'Sullivan added: "He said his life
OL,8,Fhad been ruined by the deceased and he
OL,9,Fblamed her for his son's suicide."
OL,11,FThe prosecutor said Suter then called
OL,12,Fhis second wife, Diane, and told her
OL,13,Fhe had murdered Ms Blackwood and,
OL,14,Freferring to the indecent assault
OL,15,Fconviction, said: "I know I am going
OL,16,Fto prison, I may as well go for this."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
