OL,4,Cflowers on their son's grave, court
OL,5,Chears
OL,7,FThe family of Ms Blackwood, who lived
OL,8,Fin Lee-on-the-Solent, said in a
OL,9,Fstatement released through Hampshire
OL,10,FConstabulary: "Her daughter, brothers,
OL,11,Ftheir families and all her friends are
OL,12,Fabsolutely devastated by the loss of
OL,13,FAnn Blackwood.
OL,15,F"A loving, caring, kind-hearted mother
OL,16,Fand friend who was very popular in her
OL,17,Flocal community, she was enjoying her
OL,18,Fretirement with an active lifestyle
OL,19,Fwhich included tennis, sailing,
OL,20,Fcycling and music."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
